   3.9119029150224075`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"085dc818-9688-4cd1-8d1e-\
67ddc101bf8a"],

Cell["\<\
The disjoint  diagrams at third order are 65,664 in total. These are \
distributed as follows:
i) 7,680 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the antidiagonal;
ii) 7,680 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the diagonal;
iii) 6,528 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in both the diagonal and the \
antidiagonal;
iv) 7,680 Direct diagrams dressed in the left propagator;
v) 7,680 Direct diagrams dressed in the right propagator;
vi) 6,528 Direct diagrams dressed in both the left and the right propagator;
vii) 7,680 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator above;
viii) 7,680 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator below;
ix) 6,528 Exchange diagrams dressed in both the above and below propagator;\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8746447846491413`*^9, 3.874644822571206*^9}, {
